  "keyPointsSummary": [
    "'Fond of' means to like something a lot, showing a preference or hobby",
    "Followed by a noun or gerund (verb + ing), never base verb",
    "Formula: am/is/are + fond of + noun/V-ing",
    "Negative: am/is/are not fond of"
